description: Make the next birthday, wedding, or any special occasion you’re planning even extra memorable by inviting Mary Had a Little Party! This peachy keen retro trailer will bring its delectable selection of tasty sweets anywhere within the Houston metro area. Present your guests with a blast from the past in the form of delicious treats, like old fashioned soda floats, hand-dipped ice cream cones, banana splits, and lemonade that is freshly squeezed. And right along with the fun doo-wop vibes, the freshly popped popcorn is the ultimate cherry on top. With nostalgic noshes so delightful, an experience like this is sure to inspire quite a few quite enthused “Oh my gosh!”’s from adults and children alike.When it comes to cartin’ in heart and soul straight to your swell soirée (with a side of yummy, melodious memories), Mary Had a Little Party is the absolute bee's knees.
name: Mary Had a Little Party
